        {
          "cells": [
            {
              "raw_text": "2.4.4 操作方法   供试品溶液制备：取本品20片，研细，精密称定，精密称取①           g②           g（约相当于别嘌醇0.1g），置       ml（100ml） 量瓶中，加0.2％氢氧化钠溶液         ml（20ml），振摇15分钟使别嘌醇溶解，加水稀释至刻度，摇匀，滤过；精密量取续滤液        ml（5ml），置      ml（50ml）量瓶中，加盐酸溶液（9→1000 ）稀释至刻度，摇匀；再精密量取续滤液       ml（5ml），置      ml（50ml）量瓶中，加盐酸溶液（9→1000 ）稀释至刻度，摇匀，作为供试品溶液。测定法：取上述溶液，照紫外-可见分光光度法(通则0401)，在250nm±2nm的波长处测定吸光度,  按 C5H4N4O的吸收系数（E1%1cm）为571计算。2.3.4.1 称重",
              "parts": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "2.4.4 操作方法"
                },
                {
                  "type": "line",
                  "field_key": "layout/allopurinol/packaging/content/t0_r14_c0_p0_line",
                  "width": "36px"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "供试品溶液制备：取本品20片，研细，精密称定，精密称取①"
                },
                {
                  "type": "line",
                  "field_key": "layout/allopurinol/packaging/content/t0_r14_c0_p1_line",
                  "width": "77px"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "g②"
                },
                {
                  "type": "line",
                  "field_key": "layout/allopurinol/packaging/content/t0_r14_c0_p2_line",
                  "width": "77px"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "g（约相当于别嘌醇0.1g），置"
                },
                {
                  "type": "line",
                  "field_key": "layout/allopurinol/packaging/content/t0_r14_c0_p3_line",
                  "width": "49px"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "ml（100ml） 量瓶中，加0.2％氢氧化钠溶液"
                },
                {
                  "type": "line",
                  "field_key": "layout/allopurinol/packaging/content/t0_r14_c0_p4_line",
                  "width": "63px"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "ml（20ml），振摇15分钟使别嘌醇溶解，加水稀释至刻度，摇匀，滤过；精密量取续滤液"
                },
                {
                  "type": "line",
                  "field_key": "layout/allopurinol/packaging/content/t0_r14_c0_p5_line",
                  "width": "56px"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "ml（5ml），置"
                },
                {
                  "type": "line",
                  "field_key": "layout/allopurinol/packaging/content/t0_r14_c0_p6_line",
                  "width": "42px"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "ml（50ml）量瓶中，加盐酸溶液（9→1000 ）稀释至刻度，摇匀；再精密量取续滤液"
                },
                {
                  "type": "line",
                  "field_key": "layout/allopurinol/packaging/content/t0_r14_c0_p7_line",
                  "width": "49px"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "ml（5ml），置"
                },
                {
